## AdventureWorks Data Dictionary

This document describes the structure of the AdventureWorks database tables used in this project.

---

## Sales Table

| Column Name | Data Type | Nullable | Description |
|-------------|-----------|----------|-------------|
| OrderDate | TEXT | YES | Date when the order was placed |
| StockDate | TEXT | YES | Date when the product was stocked |
| OrderNumber | TEXT | YES | Unique order number |
| ProductKey | INT | YES | Foreign key referencing the Products table |
| CustomerKey | INT | YES | Foreign key referencing the Customer table |
| TerritoryKey | INT | YES | Foreign key referencing the Territories table |
| OrderLineItem | INT | YES | Line item number within an order |
| OrderQuantity | INT | YES | Quantity of products ordered |

---

## Customer Table

| Column Name | Data Type | Nullable | Description |
|-------------|-----------|----------|-------------|
| CustomerKey | INT | YES | Unique identifier for each customer |
| Prefix | TEXT | YES | Customer title (Mr., Mrs., etc.) |
| FirstName | TEXT | YES | Customer's first name |
| LastName | TEXT | YES | Customer's last name |
| BirthDate | TEXT | YES | Customer's date of birth |
| MaritalStatus | TEXT | YES | Customer's marital status |
| Gender | TEXT | YES | Customer's gender |
| EmailAddress | TEXT | YES | Customer's email address |
| AnnualIncome | TEXT | YES | Customer's annual income |
| TotalChildren | INT | YES | Number of children |
| EducationLevel | TEXT | YES | Highest education level |
| Occupation | TEXT | YES | Customer's occupation |
| HomeOwner | TEXT | YES | Indicates whether the customer owns a home |

---

## Product Categories Table

| Column Name | Data Type | Nullable | Description |
|-------------|-----------|----------|-------------|
| ProductCategoryKey | INT | YES | Unique identifier for each product category |
| CategoryName | TEXT | YES | Name of the product category (e.g., Bikes, Clothing, Accessories) |

---

## Product Subcategories Table

| Column Name | Data Type | Nullable | Description |
|-------------|-----------|----------|-------------|
| ProductSubcategoryKey | INT | YES | Unique identifier for each product subcategory |
| SubcategoryName | TEXT | YES | Name of the product subcategory (e.g., Mountain Bikes, Road Bikes) |
| ProductCategoryKey | INT | YES | Foreign key referencing the Product Categories table |

---

## Products Table

| Column Name | Data Type | Nullable | Description |
|-------------|-----------|----------|-------------|
| ProductKey | INT | YES | Unique identifier for each product |
| ProductSubcategoryKey | INT | YES | Foreign key referencing the Product Subcategories table |
| ProductSKU | TEXT | YES | Stock Keeping Unit (SKU) used to uniquely identify the product |
| ProductName | TEXT | YES | Name of the product |
| ModelName | TEXT | YES | Model name of the product |
| ProductDescription | TEXT | YES | Description of the product |
| ProductColor | TEXT | YES | Color of the product |
| ProductSize | TEXT | YES | Size of the product |
| ProductStyle | TEXT | YES | Style or variant of the product |
| ProductCost | DOUBLE | YES | Cost incurred to manufacture or procure the product |
| ProductPrice | DOUBLE | YES | Selling price of the product |

---

## Territories Table

| Column Name | Data Type | Nullable | Description |
|-------------|-----------|----------|-------------|
| SalesTerritoryKey | INT | YES | Unique identifier for each sales territory |
| Region | TEXT | YES | Region where the sales occurred |
| Country | TEXT | YES | Country of the sales territory |
| Continent | TEXT | YES | Continent to which the sales territory belongs |
